---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Content from '@components/Content.astro';
---
<BaseLayout 
    title="About"
    description="Learn about Behelit Systems, our mission, vision, and the global intelligence network that powers our advanced security services.">
    <Content>
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto pt-28 md:pt-40">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
                <!-- Text Content -->
                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-sm uppercase text-gray-500 font-bold mb-4">About /</h2>
                    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight leading-tight">
                        We are a cybersecurity firm engineering unyielding resilience from silicon to people.
                    </h1>
                </div>
                <!-- Image Placeholder -->
                <div class="w-full h-80 bg-gray-200 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                    <span class="text-gray-400">Image Placeholder</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Separator -->
            <hr class="border-t border-gray-300 my-20 md:my-28" />

            <!-- Detailed Sections -->
            <div class="space-y-16">
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-base">
                    <div class="md:col-span-1">
                        <h2 class="font-bold mb-2">Our Mission</h2>
                    </div>
                    <div class="md:col-span-2 text-gray-700 space-y-4">
                        <p>To revolutionize security posture by meticulously uncovering and neutralizing critical vulnerabilities in hardware and the human element, providing unparalleled, actionable insights, and fostering a collaborative, resilient cybersecurity ecosystem.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <hr class="border-t border-gray-200" />

                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-base">
                    <div class="md:col-span-1">
                        <h2 class="font-bold mb-2">Our Vision</h2>
                    </div>
                    <div class="md:col-span-2 text-gray-700 space-y-4">
                        <p>To be the leading and most trusted authority in full-spectrum hardware and human factor security in Southeast Asia and beyond, setting new standards for adversarial simulation and defensive hardening.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <hr class="border-t border-gray-200" />

                 <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-base">
                    <div class="md:col-span-1">
                        <h2 class="font-bold mb-2">Our Approach</h2>
                    </div>
                    <div class="md:col-span-2 text-gray-700 space-y-4">
                        <p>Our foundation is unparalleled global collaboration. We actively forge partnerships with elite researchers from the world's most prestigious security communities, including DEF CON, Black Hat, and Hardwear.io. This formidable global intelligence is directly channeled into our client engagements and cutting-edge training programs.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <hr class="border-t border-gray-200" />

                 <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-base">
                    <div class="md:col-span-1">
                        <h2 class="font-bold mb-2">The Founder</h2>
                    </div>
                    <div class="md:col-span-2 text-gray-700 space-y-4">
                        <p>Behelit Systems was launched in July 2025 by Chew Zhan Hong (Gabe), a security consultant with deep expertise in full-spectrum hardware security, physical penetration testing, and advanced social engineering.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </Content>
</BaseLayout>